  "prompt": "Which is the best modular kitchen in india?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" modular kitchen in India can be subjective, as it depends on individual preferences, budget, design needs, and functionality. However, several popular brands are renowned for their quality, designs, and customer service in the modular kitchen segment:\n\n1. **H\u00e4fele**: A well-known international brand offering a wide range of modular kitchen solutions, H\u00e4fele is known for its innovative designs and quality hardware.\n\n2. **Godrej Interio**: A trusted name in furniture, Godrej Interio offers modular kitchens that combine aesthetics with functionality.\n\n3. **Kitchen Craft**: This brand specializes in modular kitchens with a focus on contemporary designs and high-quality materials.\n\n4. **Hettich**: Known for high-quality fittings, Hettich also offers modular kitchen solutions that ensure durability and style.\n\n5. **Livspace**: A tech-enabled home interior platform, Livspace provides customized modular kitchen solutions based on customer preferences and requirements.\n\n6. **OLX Kitchens**: They focus on personalized modular kitchen solutions with a wide range of materials and finishes.\n\n7. **Interior Company**: Known for their chic designs and modern amenities, they offer modular kitchens tailored to individual needs.\n\n8. **Adorn Spaces**: They provide stylish and functional modular kitchens, focusing on innovative storage solutions.\n\nWhen choosing a modular kitchen, consider factors like materials used, customization options, design aesthetics, warranty, and after-sales service. It's advisable to visit showrooms, consult with professionals, and check customer reviews to make an informed decision.",
